WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.610 --> 00:00:02.670
Welcome to the lymphatic system.

1
00:00:05.019 --> 00:00:06.400
Do you know the key to good health?

2
00:00:06.659 --> 00:00:07.360
Think again.

3
00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:10.779
When it comes to wellness,

4
00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:13.079
we focus on food and workouts,

5
00:00:13.439 --> 00:00:14.180
superfoods,

6
00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:14.960
supplements,

7
00:00:15.079 --> 00:00:16.059
detoxes,

8
00:00:16.559 --> 00:00:18.120
all promising better immunity,

9
00:00:18.239 --> 00:00:19.250
glowing skin,

10
00:00:19.399 --> 00:00:20.280
and more energy.

11
00:00:22.610 --> 00:00:26.530
But what if true long-lasting health isn't about what you add to your routine,

12
00:00:26.899 --> 00:00:30.149
but about a system that's been working silently inside you all along?

13
00:00:32.418 --> 00:00:34.479
Your body has a personal maintenance team.

14
00:00:34.779 --> 00:00:36.459
It's called the lymphatic system,

15
00:00:36.619 --> 00:00:37.939
your body's natural filter,

16
00:00:38.099 --> 00:00:39.400
internal defense mechanism,

17
00:00:39.529 --> 00:00:40.599
and garbage collector.

18
00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:43.959
Unexplained fatigue,

19
00:00:44.180 --> 00:00:45.020
constant bloating,

20
00:00:45.099 --> 00:00:45.939
swollen glands,

21
00:00:46.060 --> 00:00:47.840
falling sick again and again,

22
00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:50.799
these are often signs of a sluggish lymphatic system.